        {
            "title": "台股第3日回吐 今再跌0.96%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股連續第3日回吐，台灣加權指數今日高開低收，且以全日低位收市，報38926點，跌376點或0.96%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15943687-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e7%ac%ac3%e6%97%a5%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e4%bb%8a%e5%86%8d%e8%b7%8c0-96",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230810_FI_source-web_TaiwanStock2-704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 13:37:47",
