            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滙豐及中銀港元最優惠利率維持5厘　渣打香港維持5.25厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本港三大發鈔銀行維持最優惠利率不變。滙豐及中銀香港的港元最優惠利率均維持於5釐，渣打香港則維持於5.25釐。三家銀行的港元儲蓄存款利率亦維持不變。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15943205-%e6%bb%99%e8%b1%90%e5%8f%8a%e4%b8%ad%e9%8a%80%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%9c%80%e5%84%aa%e6%83%a0%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%87%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%815%e5%8e%98%e3%80%80%e6%b8%a3%e6%89%93%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%815",
